data.description: Motivated Sellers! Sellers are relocating and are ready to sell! What makes this home so unique is it includes a finished Guest Casita in the back yard adding an additional 544 square feet with a bedroom, bathroom, kitchen & living space - bringing the total to over 2300 finished square feet (property has 4 bedrooms & 3 bathrooms total)! Completely updated kitchen with new cabinets, appliances, countertops & backsplash! The solar panels bring the electricity bill down immensely. Large fenced backyard includes a huge above ground pool! Unfinished basement so you can add your own touch to the home. HVAC & furnace replaced last year! Don't miss out on this one-of-a-kind property in Pueblo West!
